The '''Thixian Seven''' was a type of four-person [[Cruiser/Legends|cruiser]] manufactured by<ref name="ShadowHunter">''[[Darth Maul: Shadow Hunter]]''</ref> [[Alderaan Royal Engineers]]<ref name="ARE">''[[Darth Maul: Shadow Hunter]]'' establishes that the Thixian Seven was manufactured by "ARE," which {{CSWECite|I|40|ARE}} in turn establishes to stand for [[Alderaan Royal Engineers]].</ref> by [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]].<ref name="Date">''[[The Essential Reader's Companion]]'' dates the events of ''[[Darth Maul: Shadow Hunter]]'', which includes the appearance of a Thixian Seven, to [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]].</ref>

